law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 69, effective December 1, 1972. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective June 18, 1970. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 28, effective June 19, 1952.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: New registration required when name changed -- Transfer of registration on change of residence -- Utility companies to report change of address of customers.
